    "We generated images of five Chinese-style living room designs using these models and performed a visual comparison.",
    "The generated images are shown in Fig. 7.",
    "By comparing these images, we can evaluate the differences in the effectiveness of different models in generating Chinese-style living rooms.",
    "This comparison will help us understand the strengths and areas for improvement of our diffusion model in generating interior designs.",
    "By observing Fig. 7, we have drawn several conclusions regarding the performance of different methods."
  ]
